skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: train my bird peekaboo
des:
This skill repeats 'Peekaboo' 50 times to train your bird to say 'Peekaboo'. 
You can put the skill on a alexa routine to schedule it to play several times a day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
